# CSS  - 11

## -
 3D `perspective`  z=0  3D 
- `perspective: none | length;`
- `length` (px) 
-  3D  `transform: perspective(length);` 

****
```html
<div class="perspective-container">
  <div class="box p-box1">Box 1</div>
  <div class="box p-box2">Box 2</div>
</div>
<style>
.perspective-container {
  width: 200px;
  height: 200px;
  border: 1px solid #ccc;
  margin: 50px;
  perspective: 300px; /*  */
}
.box {
  width: 100px;
  height: 100px;
  background-color: lightcoral;
  margin: 50px auto;
  text-align: center;
  line-height: 100px;
  transition: transform 1s;
}
.p-box1:hover {
  transform: rotateY(45deg);
}
.p-box2 {
  background-color: lightseagreen;
}
.p-box2:hover {
  transform: translateZ(50px) rotateY(45deg); /*  */
}
</style>
```

## -
 `transform`  `translate3d(x, y, z)`  `translateZ(z)` 
- `transform: translate3d(tx, ty, tz);` XYZ  tx, ty, tz
- `transform: translateX(tx);` X 
- `transform: translateY(ty);` Y 
- `transform: translateZ(tz);` Z  `perspective`  Z 

****
```html
<div class="perspective-container">
  <div class="box translate3d-example">TranslateZ</div>
</div>
<style>
/* .perspective-container  .box  */
.translate3d-example:hover {
  transform: translateZ(100px); /* 100px */
}
</style>
```

## -
 `transform`  `rotate3d(x, y, z, angle)`  `rotateX(angle)`, `rotateY(angle)`, `rotateZ(angle)` 
- `transform: rotate3d(x, y, z, angle);` `[x, y, z]` 
- `transform: rotateX(angle);` X 
- `transform: rotateY(angle);` Y 
- `transform: rotateZ(angle);` Z  2D  `rotate(angle)`
  `rotateX`  `rotateY`  `perspective` 

****
```html
<div class="perspective-container">
  <div class="box rotateX-example">RotateX</div>
  <div class="box rotateY-example">RotateY</div>
</div>
<style>
/* .perspective-container  .box  */
.rotateX-example { background-color: lightgoldenrodyellow; }
.rotateX-example:hover {
  transform: rotateX(60deg); /* X60 */
}
.rotateY-example { background-color: lightpink; }
.rotateY-example:hover {
  transform: rotateY(60deg); /* Y60 */
}
</style>
```

## - transform-style
`transform-style`  3D 
- `transform-style: flat;` (): 
- `transform-style: preserve-3d;` 3D  3D  `transform`  `transform: none;` 

****
```html
<div class="cube-container">
  <div class="cube">
    <div class="face front">Front</div>
    <div class="face back">Back</div>
    <div class="face right">Right</div>
    <div class="face left">Left</div>
    <div class="face top">Top</div>
    <div class="face bottom">Bottom</div>
  </div>
</div>
<style>
.cube-container {
  width: 200px;
  height: 200px;
  margin: 100px;
  perspective: 800px; /*  */
}
.cube {
  width: 100%;
  height: 100%;
  position: relative;
  transform-style: preserve-3d; /* 3D */
  transform: rotateX(-30deg) rotateY(-45deg);
  transition: transform 2s;
}
.cube:hover {
  transform: rotateX(-30deg) rotateY(-135deg);
}
.face {
  position: absolute;
  width: 200px;
  height: 200px;
  border: 1px solid grey;
  background-color: rgba(173, 216, 230, 0.7); /* lightblue with alpha */
  font-size: 20px;
  text-align: center;
  line-height: 200px;
  color: black;
  opacity: 0.8;
}
.front  { transform: translateZ(100px); }
.back   { transform: rotateY(180deg) translateZ(100px); }
.right  { transform: rotateY(90deg) translateZ(100px); }
.left   { transform: rotateY(-90deg) translateZ(100px); }
.top    { transform: rotateX(90deg) translateZ(100px); }
.bottom { transform: rotateX(-90deg) translateZ(100px); }
</style>
```

## -
 `transform`  `scale3d(sx, sy, sz)`  `scaleZ(sz)` 
- `transform: scale3d(sx, sy, sz);` XYZ  sx, sy, sz 
- `transform: scaleX(sx);` X 
- `transform: scaleY(sy);` Y 
- `transform: scaleZ(sz);` Z `scaleZ`  3D 

****
```html
<div class="perspective-container">
  <div class="box scale3d-example">Scale3D</div>
</div>
<style>
/* .perspective-container  .box  */
.scale3d-example { background-color: mediumpurple; }
.scale3d-example:hover {
  transform: scale3d(1.2, 1.2, 1.5) rotateY(30deg); /*  */
}
</style>
```

## 

### key-frame
`@keyframes`  CSS 
- 
  ```css
  @keyframes animationname {
    from { /* CSS  */ } /* 0% */
    percentage { /* CSS  */ } /*  50% */
    to { /* CSS  */ }   /* 100% */
  }
  ```
- `animationname`  `animation-name` 
- `from`  `0%``to`  `100%`

****
```css
@keyframes colorAndMove {
  0% {
    background-color: red;
    transform: translateX(0);
  }
  50% {
    background-color: yellow;
    transform: translateX(100px);
  }
  100% {
    background-color: blue;
    transform: translateX(0);
  }
}
```

###  animation
 `@keyframes`  `animation` 

- `animation-name`:  `@keyframes` 
- `animation-duration`:  (e.g., `2s`, `500ms`)
- `animation-timing-function`:  (e.g., `linear`, `ease`, `ease-in`, `ease-out`, `ease-in-out`, `cubic-bezier()`, `steps()`)
- `animation-delay`: 
- `animation-iteration-count`:  (e.g., `3`, `infinite`)
- `animation-direction`:  (e.g., `normal`, `reverse`, `alternate`, `alternate-reverse`)
- `animation-fill-mode`:  (e.g., `none`, `forwards`, `backwards`, `both`)
- `animation-play-state`:  (e.g., `running`, `paused`)

****
`animation: name duration timing-function delay iteration-count direction fill-mode play-state;`

** `colorAndMove` **
```html
<div class="animated-box"></div>
<style>
.animated-box {
  width: 100px;
  height: 100px;
  background-color: red; /*  */
  animation-name: colorAndMove;
  animation-duration: 4s;
  animation-timing-function: ease-in-out;
  animation-iteration-count: infinite;
  animation-direction: alternate;
}
/* @keyframes colorAndMove  */
</style>
```

### 

 `@keyframes`  `transform: translateX()` 

****
```html
<div class="marquee-container">
  <div class="marquee-content">... ... ...</div>
</div>
<style>
.marquee-container {
  width: 300px; /*  */
  overflow: hidden; /*  */
  border: 1px solid black;
  background-color: #f0f0f0;
}
.marquee-content {
  display: inline-block; /*  */
  white-space: nowrap; /*  */
  padding-left: 100%; /*  */
  animation: marquee-scroll 15s linear infinite;
}
@keyframes marquee-scroll {
  0% {
    transform: translateX(0); /* padding-left:100% */
  }
  100% {
    transform: translateX(-200%); /*  +  */
                                  /* JS */
  }
}
/* JS
   CSStranslateX
   .marquee-content600px300px
    translateX(0)  translateX(-600px - 300px) = translateX(-900px)

*/
</style>
```
** ():**
```html
<div class="marquee-container-improved">
  <span class="marquee-text-improved">...&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span>
  <span class="marquee-text-improved">...&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span> <!--  -->
</div>
<style>
.marquee-container-improved {
  width: 300px;
  overflow: hidden;
  border: 1px solid black;
  background-color: #f0f0f0;
  white-space: nowrap; /*  nowrap */
}
.marquee-text-improved {
  display: inline-block;
  animation: marquee-scroll-improved 10s linear infinite;
}
@keyframes marquee-scroll-improved {
  0% {
    transform: translateX(0%);
  }
  100% {
    transform: translateX(-100%); /*  */
  }
}
</style>
```


### 

#### 
 (Sprite Animation) 

CSS  `background-position`  `steps()` 

1.  **** `div``overflow: hidden;`
2.  **** `@keyframes` `background-position-x` ( `y`) 
3.  **** `div` `animation-timing-function: steps(N);` N `steps(N)`  N 

****
 `sprite.png` 800px 8  100px 
```html
<div class="sprite-animation"></div>
<style>
.sprite-animation {
  width: 100px;  /*  */
  height: 150px; /*  */
  background-image: url('path/to/your/sprite.png'); /*  */
  background-repeat: no-repeat;
  animation-name: playSprite;
  animation-duration: 0.8s; /* 80.1s */
  animation-timing-function: steps(8); /* 8 */
  animation-iteration-count: infinite;
}

@keyframes playSprite {
  from { background-position-x: 0px; }
  to { background-position-x: -800px; } /*  */
}
</style>
```
**:** 8

#### 
 `animation` 
`animation: animation1_settings, animation2_settings, ...;`

`animation-name: name1, name2;`
`animation-duration: duration1, duration2;`


****
```html
<div class="multi-animated-box">Multi Animation</div>
<style>
@keyframes changeColorMulti {
  0% { background-color: gold; }
  50% { background-color: orangered; }
  100% { background-color: gold; }
}

@keyframes rotateBoxMulti {
  from { transform: rotate(0deg); }
  to { transform: rotate(360deg); }
}

.multi-animated-box {
  width: 150px;
  height: 150px;
  margin: 50px;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  /*  */
  animation-name: changeColorMulti, rotateBoxMulti;
  animation-duration: 3s, 5s;
  animation-timing-function: ease-in-out, linear;
  animation-iteration-count: infinite, infinite;
  animation-direction: alternate, normal;
}
</style>
```
